definition.text: Now that everything's clear, let's do the switch and get ready for what comes next!

paragraphs.text: This is what you need to do:
Go back to the footer and select Plugins/Docs as your Current Branch.
You will get a page explaining what is being done. Then you will get another page telling you of the outcome explaining you must restart the app.
Do close the app and restart it (browser & console).

Find the Contribute to Superalgos Tutorial in the bottom-right corner of the workspace and select Resume on the menu! If Resume doesn't work, find the Welcome Back! step under the Branches Topic and click Play on the menu!
